en_225420_0	Senior Additional Solicitor General Sanjaya Rajaratnam has been appointed as the Acting Solicitor General.
en_225420_1	The Attorney General's Coordinator, State Counsel Nishara Jayaratne said that the appointment was made by the Public Service Commission with immediate effect.
en_225420_2	The services of Solicitor General Dilrukshi Dias Wickremasinghe was suspended following a notification given by the Public Service Commission recently.
en_225420_3	It was based on a telephone conversation between Dilrukshi Dias Wickremasinghe, former Director General of the Bribery Commission and the Chairman of Avantgarde, Nissanka Senadhipathi.
